Ri referred to the joint statement made by Kim Jong Un and Donald Trump at the first summit between a U.S. incumbent president and a North Korean leader in Singapore on June 12, in which Kim pledged to work on the “denuclearization of the Korean peninsula,” while promising guarantees for North Korea’s security.
